    "en": {
      "title": "The IOC increased similarly",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ceylon Petroleum Corporation has increased fuel prices as follows. Similarly, the IOC has similarly increased fuel prices.",
        "Accordingly, the price of a liter of 92 octane petrol will be increased by 50 rupees and the new price will be 470 rupees.",
        "The price of 95 octane petrol has been increased by Rs 100 per liter to Rs 550 per liter.",
        "Meanwhile, the price of a liter of auto diesel has been increased by 60 rupees to 460 rupees.",
        "The price of Lanka Super Diesel will be increased by 75 rupees and the new price will be revised to 520 rupees."
      ],
